# Dynamic phrase list
# The file lists/turkish_spam_phrases.txt is provided for manual reference
# and maintenance.  SpamAssassin body rules cannot be loaded from external
# lists, so phrases must be added as explicit rules above when needed.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
